container_info.post_install_tip: Add awesome icons to your documents by choosing them directly from the Flaticon for the Gsuit (GDocs). Open the add on, search the icon you need in the search bar, and add it to your document by clicking on it.

name: Flaticon for Gsuit (GDocs)
description: With Flaticon for Gsuit (GDocs) you will have all the power of Flaticon (largest icon database in the world) in your Google Docs.
